\id ZEP - Biblica® Open Luganda Contemporary Bible 2014
\h Zeffaniya
\toc1 Zeffaniya
\toc2 Zeffaniya
\toc3 Zef
\mt2 Ekitabo Ekiyitibwa
\mt1 Zeffaniya
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Zeffaniya mutabani wa Kuusi, muzzukulu wa Gedaliya, muzzukulu wa Amaliya, muzzukulu wa Keezeekiya, mu mirembe gya Yosiya mutabani wa Amoni, Kabaka wa Yuda.
\s1 Okulabula kw’Omusango n’Okuzikirizibwa kwa Yuda
\q1 
\v 2 “Ndizikiririza ddala byonna okuva ku nsi,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.
\q1 
\v 3 “Ndizikiriza abantu wamu n’ensolo;
\q2 ndizikiriza ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga
\q2 n’ebyennyanja;
\q1 ababi balisigaza ntuumu ya kafakalimbo;
\q2 bwe ndimalawo abantu okuva ku nsi,”
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.
\q1 
\v 4 Ndigololera ku Yuda omukono gwange,
\q2 era ne ku abo bonna abali mu Yerusaalemi;
\q1 era ekitundu kya Baali ekifisseewo n’ennyumba ya Bakemali,
\q2 bakabona abasinza ebifaananyi, ndibazikiriza okuva mu kifo kino,
\q1 
\v 5 abo abavuunamira eggye ery’omu ggulu
\q2 ku nnyumba waggulu,
\q1 ne balisinza n’abo abalayira mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 ate nga balayira ne mu linnya lya Malukamu,
\q1 
\v 6 abo abadda emabega obutagoberera \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 wadde abo abatamunoonya newaakubadde okumwebuuzaako.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Siriikirira awali \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda,
\q2 kubanga olunaku lwa \nd Mukama\nd* luli kumpi.
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* ategese ssaddaaka,
\q2 era atukuzizza abagenyi be.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Ku lunaku olwa ssaddaaka ya \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 ndibonereza abakungu
\q2 n’abaana ba Kabaka,
\q1 n’abo bonna abambadde
\q2 ebyambalo ebitasaana.
\q1 
\v 9 Awo ku lunaku olwo ndibonereza
\q2 abo bonna abeewala okulinnya ku muziziko,
\q1 n’abo abajjuza ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* waabwe
\q2 ebikolwa eby’obukambwe n’obulimba.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Ku lunaku olwo, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 eddoboozi ery’okukaaba liriwulikika ku Mulyango ogw’Ebyennyanja,
\q2 okukaaba okuva ku luuyi olwokubiri,
\q2 n’okubwatuka okunene okuva ku nsozi.
\q1 
\v 11 Mwekaabireko, mmwe abali mu matwale g’akatale;
\q2 abasuubuzi bammwe bonna zibasanze,
\q2 n’abo abeebinika ffeeza balizikirizibwa.
\q1 
\v 12 Awo olulituuka mu biro ebyo ndimulisa Yerusaalemi n’ettabaaza nga nnoonya,
\q2 mbonereze abo bonna abalagajjavu
\q2 abali ng’omwenge ogutanasengejjebwa,
\q1 abalowooza nti \nd Mukama\nd*
\q2 talibaako ne ky’akolawo.
\q1 
\v 13 Obugagga bwabwe bulinyagibwa,
\q2 n’ennyumba zaabwe zimenyebwemenyebwe.
\q1 Ne bwe balizimba ennyumba
\q2 tebalizituulamu,
\q1 era balisimba ennimiro ez’emizabbibu nazo
\q2 tebalinywa wayini wamu.
\s1 Olunaku lwa \nd Mukama\nd* Olukulu
\q1 
\v 14 Olunaku lwa \nd Mukama\nd* olukulu luli kumpi;
\q2 ddala lunaatera okutuuka.
\q1 Wuliriza! Omulwanyi alikaabira eyo ng’aliko obuyinike bungi,
\q2 n’okukaaba ku lunaku lwa \nd Mukama\nd* kujja kuba kungi nnyo.
\q1 
\v 15 Olunaku olwo lunaku lwa busungu,
\q2 lunaku lwa buyinike n’okulaba ennaku,
\q1 lunaku lwa mutawaana n’okuzikirira,
\q2 olunaku olw’ekikome n’ekizikiza,
\q2 olunaku lw’ebire n’ekizikiza ekikutte ennyo;
\q1 
\v 16 olunaku olw’okufuuwa ekkondeere n’okulangirira olutalo
\q2 ku bibuga ebiriko ebigo
\q2 n’eri eminaala emigulumivu.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 Ndireeta, obuyinike ku bantu,
\q2 batambule ng’abazibe b’amaaso,
\q2 kubanga bakoze ebibi mu maaso ga \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q1 omusaayi gwabwe guliyiyibwa ng’enfuufu,
\q2 n’ebyenda byabwe bivundire kungulu.
\q1 
\v 18 Effeeza yaabwe ne zaabu yaabwe
\q2 tebiriyinza kubataasa
\q2 ku lunaku olw’obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd*.
\b
\q1 Ensi yonna erizikirizibwa
\q2 omuliro gw’obuggya bwe,
\q1 era alimalirawo ddala
\q2 abo bonna abali mu nsi.
\c 2
\s1 Abalabe ba Isirayiri Basalirwa Omusango
\q1 
\v 1 Mukuŋŋaane, weewaawo, mukuŋŋaane,
\q2 mmwe eggwanga eritalina nsonyi,
\q1 
\v 2 ekiseera ekyategekebwa nga tekinnatuuka,
\q2 olunaku ne luba ng’ebisusunku ebifuumulibwa,
\q1 obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* nga tebunnabatuukako,
\q2 ng’olunaku olw’obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* terunnabatuukako.
\q1 
\v 3 Munoonye \nd Mukama\nd*, mmwe mwenna abawombeefu ab’omu nsi,
\q2 abakola by’alagira;
\q1 munoonye obutuukirivu n’obuwombeefu;
\q2 mpozzi mulikwekebwa
\q2 ku lunaku olw’obusungu bwe.
\s1 Obubaka eri Abafirisuuti
\q1 
\v 4 Gaza kirirekebwawo,
\q2 ne Asukulooni kiriba matongo:
\q1 abantu ba Asudodi baligobebwamu mu ttuntu,
\q2 ne Ekuloni kirisimbulibwa.
\q1 
\v 5 Zibasanze mmwe ababeera ku lubalama lw’ennyanja,
\q2 eggwanga ery’Abakeresi!
\q1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kikwolekedde,
\q2 ggwe Kanani, ensi ey’Abafirisuuti.
\q1 Ndikuzikiriza
\q2 so tewaliba asigalawo.
\q1 
\v 6 Olubalama lw’ennyanja ab’Akeresi gye babeera
\q2 luliba malundiro g’abasumba n’ebisulo by’endiga.
\q1 
\v 7 Olubalama lw’ennyanja luliba lwa kitundu ky’ennyumba ya Yuda ekyasigalawo
\q2 era we banaalundiranga,
\q1 ne mu nnyumba za Asukulooni
\q2 mwe banaagalamiranga akawungeezi.
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe alibalabirira,
\q2 n’akomyawo obugagga bwabwe.
\s1 Obubaka eri Abamowaabu n’Abamoni
\q1 
\v 8 Mpulidde okuvuma kwa Mowaabu
\q2 n’okusekerera kw’Abamoni
\q1 kwe bavumye abantu bange
\q2 ne batiisatiisa ensi yaabwe.
\q1 
\v 9 Kale nga bwe ndi omulamu,
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Ayinzabyonna, Katonda wa Isirayiri,
\q1 ddala Mowaabu aliba nga Sodomu,
\q2 n’abaana ba Amoni nga Ggomola,
\q1 ekifo emyennyango kye gyemala, n’ebirombe by’omunnyo,
\q2 amatongo agolubeerera. Balinyagibwa abantu bange abaliba basigaddewo,
\q1 n’ekitundu ky’eggwanga lyange ekifisseewo kiritwala ensi yaabwe.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Eno y’eriba empeera yaabwe olw’amalala gaabwe,
\q2 kubanga bavumye ne banyooma abantu ba \nd Mukama\nd* Ayinzabyonna.
\q1 
\v 11 \nd Mukama\nd* aliba wa ntiisa gye bali
\q2 bw’alizikiriza bakatonda bonna ab’ensi.
\q1 Amawanga gonna ag’oku mbalama zonna galimusinza,
\q2 buli muntu ng’asinziira mu nsi ye.
\s1 Obubaka eri Abaesiyopiya
\q1 
\v 12 Nammwe Abaesiyopiya, mulittibwa n’ekitala kyange.
\s1 Obubaka eri Obwasuli
\q1 
\v 13 Aligololera omukono gwe ku bukiikakkono
\q2 n’azikiriza Obwasuli;
\q1 n’afuula Nineeve amatongo
\q2 era ekikalu ng’eddungu.
\q1 
\v 14 Ente n’endiga zinaagalamiranga wakati mu kyo,
\q2 n’ensolo zonna eza buli kika:
\q1 ekiwuugulu era ne nnamunnungu
\q2 banaasulanga ku mpagi zaakyo.
\q1 Amaloboozi gaabyo ganaawulikikanga mu madirisa;
\q2 kafakalimbo ajjudde mu miryango,
\q2 n’emikiikiro egy’emivule giryelulwa.
\q1 
\v 15 Kino kye kibuga ekya kyetwala,
\q2 ekyayogeranga mu mutima gwakyo nti,
\q2 Nze we ndi, tewali mulala wabula nze:
\q1 nga kifuuse bifulukwa,
\q2 ekifo ensolo ez’omu nsiko we zigalamira!
\q1 Buli muntu akiyitako aneesoozanga
\q2 n’akinyoomoola.
\c 3
\s1 Obujeemu bwa Yerusaalemi
\q1 
\v 1 Zikisanze ekibuga ekijooga,
\q2 ekijeemu era ekyonoonefu!
\q1 
\v 2 Tekigondera ddoboozi lya \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 wadde okukkiriza okubuulirirwa;
\q1 tekyesiga \nd Mukama\nd*;
\q2 wadde okusemberera Katonda waakyo.
\q1 
\v 3 Abakungu baakyo mpologoma eziwuluguma,
\q2 era n’abalamuzi baakyo misege gya kiro,
\q2 bakirimululu abatafissaawo kantu.
\q1 
\v 4 Bannabbi baakyo si ba buvunaanyizibwa
\q2 era ba nkwe;
\q1 bakabona baakyo baweebuusizza ekifo ekitukuvu,
\q2 era bamenya amateeka.
\q1 
\v 5 \nd Mukama\nd* ali wakati mu kyo, mutuukirivu
\q2 era tasobya.
\q1 Buli nkya alamula mu bwenkanya,
\q2 era buli lukya talemwa;
\q2 naye atali mutuukirivu taswala.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “Nsanyizzaawo amawanga,
\q2 era ebigo byabwe bifufuggaziddwa;
\q1 nzisizza enguudo zaabwe,
\q2 ne wataba ayitamu.
\q1 Ebibuga byabwe bizikiridde,
\q2 ne watabaawo muntu n’omu abeeramu.
\q1 
\v 7 Nagamba eri ekibuga nti,
\q2 ‘Ddala onontya,
\q2 era onokkiriza okubuulirirwa.’
\q1 Ennyumba zaakyo tezandimaliddwawo,
\q2 n’ebibonerezo byange byonna tebyandimutuuseeko.
\q1 Naye beesunganga nnyo
\q2 okukola ebitasaana mu byonna bye baakolanga.
\q1 
\v 8 Noolwekyo munnindirire,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.
\q2 Olunaku lwe ndiyimirira ne ntegeeza byonna
\q1 kubanga mmaliridde okukuŋŋaanya amawanga,
\q2 ndireeta obwakabaka wamu
\q1 okubayiwako obusungu bwange,
\q2 n’ekiruyi kyange kyonna.
\q1 Omuliro ogw’obuggya bwange
\q2 gulisaanyaawo ensi yonna.
\s1 Essuubi lya Isirayiri
\q1 
\v 9 “Mu biro ebyo ndirongoosa enjogera ey’amawanga;
\q2 bonna balikoowoola erinnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*,
\q2 okumuweereza n’omwoyo gumu.
\q1 
\v 10 Okuva emitala w’emigga egy’Obuwesiyopya,
\q2 abo abansinza, abantu bange abasaasaana,
\q2 balindeetera ssaddaaka.
\q1 
\v 11 Ku lunaku olwo toliswala
\q2 olw’ebyo byonna by’osobezza gye ndi:
\q1 kubanga ndiggya wakati mu ggwe
\q2 abo abeenyumiririza mu malala,
\q1 toliddayo nate kwegulumiza
\q2 ku lusozi lwange olutukuvu.
\q1 
\v 12 Naye ndireka wakati mu ggwe
\q2 abantu abakakkamu era abeetoowaze,
\q2 abo abesiga erinnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*.
\q1 
\v 13 Ekitundu kya Isirayiri ekirisigalawo tebalikola bitali bya butuukirivu
\q2 so tebalyogera bya bulimba
\q2 wadde okuba abakuusa.
\q1 Balirya, baligalamira,
\q2 so tewaliba alibatiisa.”
\s1 Oluyimba olw’Essanyu
\q1 
\v 14 Yimba, ggwe omuwala wa Sayuuni;
\q2 yogerera waggulu, ggwe Isirayiri;
\q1 sanyuka ojaguze n’omutima gwo gwonna,
\q2 ggwe omuwala wa Yerusaalemi.
\q1 
\v 15 \nd Mukama\nd* akuggyeeko ekibonerezo kyo,
\q2 agobyewo omulabe wo.
\q1 Kabaka wa Isirayiri, \nd Mukama\nd*, ali naawe;
\q2 tokyaddayo kutya kabi konna.
\q1 
\v 16 Ku lunaku olwo Yerusaalemi kirigambibwa nti,
\q2 “Totya, ggwe Sayuuni;
\q2 emikono gyo gireme okuddirira.
\q1 
\v 17 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ali naawe,
\q2 ow’amaanyi alokola:
\q1 alikusanyukira,
\q2 alikukkakkanyiza mu kwagala kwe,
\q2 alikusanyukira n’okuyimba.”
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Ennaku eyabakwatanga olw’embaga ezabakuŋŋaanyanga
\q2 ndigibaggyako;
\q2 kubanga kibafuukidde omugugu.
\q1 
\v 19 Laba, mu biro ebyo ndibonereza
\q2 abo bonna abaakubonyaabonya:
\q1 era ndinunula omulema,
\q2 ne nkuŋŋaanya n’abo abaasaasaanyizibwa;
\q1 era ndibafuula ettendo ne mbawa ekitiibwa
\q2 mu nsi zonna gye baaswazibwa.
\q1 
\v 20 Mu biro ebyo ndibakuŋŋaanya;
\q2 mu kiseera ekyo ndibazza eka.
\q1 Weewaawo ndibawa ekitiibwa n’ettendo
\q2 mu mawanga gonna ag’omu nsi zonna,
\q1 bwe ndikomyawo obugagga bwammwe
\q2 nga mulaba,”
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.
